%description
Provides two new layer types for displaying image data as layers within
the Grammar of Graphics framework. Displays images using either a
rectangle interface, with a fixed bounding box, or a point interface using
a central point and general size parameter. Images can be given as local
JPEG or PNG files, external resources, or as a list column containing
raster image data.

